---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<html lang="ja">
  <BaseHead title="idxma.net" />
  <body style="font-family: 'Zen Kaku Gothic New', sans-serif; background-color: #dcdcdc; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
    <header style="text-align: center; padding: 2rem 1rem;">

      <img src="/me-icon.png" alt="プロフィール画像" style="width: clamp(110px, 30vw, 140px); height: auto; border-radius: 50%; aspect-ratio: 4 / 3.7;" />
      <h1 style="margin: 1rem 0; font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 2rem);">kou</h1>
      <p style="margin: 0 0 2rem; font-size: clamp(0.875rem, 3vw, 1rem);">PC, 音響, デザイン, 車などがすき。<br>
      細々と暮らしています。</p>

      <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap;">
        <a href="https://github.com/idxma" target="_blank" style="text-align: center;">
          <img src="/github-icon.png" alt="GitHub" style="width: clamp(32px, 8vw, 40px); height: clamp(32px, 8vw, 40px);" />
          <div style="margin-top: 8px; font-size: clamp(0.75rem, 2.5vw, 1rem);">GitHub</div>
        </a>
        <a href="https://x.com/idxma" target="_blank" style="text-align: center;">
          <img src="/x-icon.png" alt="X" style="width: clamp(32px, 8vw, 40px); height: clamp(32px, 8vw, 40px);" />
          <div style="margin-top: 8px; font-size: clamp(0.75rem, 2.5vw, 1rem);">X</div>
        </a>
        <a href="https://keybase.io/idxma" target="_blank" style="text-align: center;">
          <img src="/keybase-icon.png" alt="keybase" style="width: clamp(32px, 8vw, 40px); height: clamp(32px, 8vw, 40px);" />
          <div style="margin-top: 8px; font-size: clamp(0.75rem, 2.5vw, 1rem);">Keybase</div>
        </a>
        <a href="https://note.com/kou_spencer" target="_blank" style="text-align: center;">
          <img src="/note-icon.png" alt="note" style="width: clamp(32px, 8vw, 40px); height: clamp(32px, 8vw, 40px);" />
          <div style="margin-top: 8px; font-size: clamp(0.75rem, 2.5vw, 1rem);">note</div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main style="padding: 1rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; font-size: clamp(0.875rem, 2.5vw, 1rem);">
        <section style="margin-bottom: 2rem; width: 100%; text-align: left;">
          <h2 style="font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 4vw, 1.5rem); font-family: inherit;">主にやっていること</h2>
          <ul style="padding-left: 1.25rem;">
      <li>System Integration</li>
      <li>Computer:
        <ul>
          <li>Infrastructure</li>
          <li>Web Development</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>Audio:
        <ul>
          <li>Amplifier: Marantz HD-AMP1</li>
          <li>Speaker: YAMAHA NS-10M (レストア済)</li>
          <li>DAC: ifi micro iDSD BL, ifi nano iDSD BL, Topping D10</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
          </ul>
    <h2 style="font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 4vw, 1.5rem); font-family: inherit;">お気に入り</h2>
    <ul style="padding-left: 1.25rem;">
      <li>Programming Language: C, C++, Python</li>
      <li>Game:
        <ul>
          <li><a href="https://jp.finalfantasyxiv.com/lodestone/character/26399914/">FF14</a></li>
          <li>Splatoon</li>
          <li>Counter-Strike 2</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>Music:
        <ul>
          <li><a href="https://youtu.be/90zQT7FnQas?si=ND1-cwjft3A5ZeXP">坂本龍一　— energy flow</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://youtu.be/-9DxpPiE458?si=eMRQU6jHwVr6T5wL">宇多田ヒカル - Automatic</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://youtu.be/T_lC2O1oIew?si=l1r5HKv2uMcHWb45">竹内まりや - Plastic Love</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://youtu.be/Da4P2uT4mVc?si=mlxl-cYiv0W4EHE7">IVE 아이브 'Baddie'</a></li>
          <iframe data-testid="embed-iframe" style="border-radius:12px" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/playlist/53ErlWSM1z0sUGFCZUwlwh?utm_source=generator&theme=0" width="100%" height="152" frameBorder="0" allowfullscreen="" allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy"></iframe>
        </ul>
      </li>
    </ul>
        <section style="margin-bottom: 2rem; width: 100%; text-align: left;">
          <h2 style="font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 4vw, 1.5rem); font-family: inherit;">過去の活動</h2>
          <ul style="padding-left: 1.25rem;">
            <li>CODE BLUE 2024 学生スタッフ</li>
            <li>セキュリティ・ミニキャンプ in 宮城 2024</li>
          </ul>
        <p style="display:flex; justify-content:center; margin: 0 0 1rem;">
        <img src="https://count.getloli.com/@idxma" alt="counter"/>
      </p>
      </section>
      </main>

      <div style="width:100%; display:flex; justify-content:center; padding:1rem 0; background:transparent;">
        <table role="presentation" style="border-collapse:collapse; max-width:960px; width:100%; margin:0 1rem;">
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding:6px; width:50%; vertical-align:top; text-align:center;">
                <a href="https://sites.google.com/view/happy-busy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="display:block;">
                  <img src="/banner1.png" alt="時間ねぇーっ！" style="width:300px; height:60; border-radius:8px; display:block;" />
                </a>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
  </body>
</html>
